{"tid":903492,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[餃子狂想曲] 咖哩餃子 茄汁豆炒蛋餃子","createTime":"2018-11-15T14:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T12:40:33.000Z","uid":133911,"like":16,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d484d9ad8836df96fb79a2d67368330b3682e3fd","tid":903492,"uid":133911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"喂大家好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐冇同大家分享我嘅餃子喇<br />\n今日就分享兩款餃子，咖哩餃子同茄汁豆炒蛋餃子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1) 咖哩餃子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9T5qEVH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9T5qEVH.png&h=d415bbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bcAhHo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bcAhHo.png&h=38b8a60a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sC4V184.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsC4V184.png&h=2a111b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/15/221930_19dfbd2f2e6329a1204af3a34e6dd83b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F15%2F221930_19dfbd2f2e6329a1204af3a34e6dd83b.png&h=96c58773&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/15/221932_a66c95bd148dfe57a121b9d55a810b14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F15%2F221932_a66c95bd148dfe57a121b9d55a810b14.png&h=dbd06039&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/15/221934_b12eb29b6287425650541661a1c8d859.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F15%2F221934_b12eb29b6287425650541661a1c8d859.png&h=e46f9c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朋友點評<br />\n係意料以內嘅味道，日式咖哩加薯仔蘿蔔洋蔥嘅組合好穩陣。唔係唔好食，但成件事好普通好唔短腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果下次再包甜餃子嘅話會再捧場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分數：6.5/10<br />\n<br />\n短腿點評<br />\n之前有喺太子食過咖哩餃子所以想試下自己包，可能因為之前已經食過一次，加上呢種日式咖哩嘅味太熟悉，所以成件事好冇驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但整體而言會覺得咖哩同餃子係夾嘅，只係驚喜欠奉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2) 茄汁豆炒蛋餃子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TEycj0q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTEycj0q.png&h=4efd54c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6FYZ0r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6FYZ0r.png&h=00b8ed11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3SsTOTO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3SsTOTO.png&h=60d5e7a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/15/223342_cef4e2fa54f2cb90989ba86aafcfd948.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F15%2F223342_cef4e2fa54f2cb90989ba86aafcfd948.png&h=0ce53717&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/15/223345_70b87abd40ba7a8608209a2c6787cfed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F15%2F223345_70b87abd40ba7a8608209a2c6787cfed.png&h=22bb8099&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/15/223348_1d792ef94a71fa092a0750cf3a130e30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F15%2F223348_1d792ef94a71fa092a0750cf3a130e30.png&h=9796f537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朋友點評<br />\n幾好食！本身茄汁豆加炒蛋呢個組合就係頹得嚟又萬無一失，將呢個萬無一失嘅組合懶係有心思咁包咗落餃子度，成件事好似忽然變得好有心思咁。而味道方面，同餃子嘅配搭幾有新鮮感，整體感覺不錯！<br />\n分數：7.5/10<br />\n<br />\n短腿點評<br />\n本身已經好鍾意食茄汁豆，再加埋炒蛋放埋落我都好鍾意嘅餃子度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成件事實在係太幸福喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加上呢個組合再配埋餃子皮成件事幾match<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家得閒都可以試下整！"},{"pid":"813241172af17a890fa3f7d13f7eee62d458fa95","tid":903492,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:52:24.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ea0d13253f0e7e9bfce7c1878df652e67f085f40","tid":903492,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"出多d post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持"},{"pid":"693f465ca57ec8f64de4e4550bb7cc3dbf87b427","tid":903492,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"又一年"},{"pid":"75e205749b4d9d9fe583b9b5686790dcaa379ac8","tid":903492,"uid":69159,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:54:44.000Z","msg":"支持出多啲post<br />\n但茄汁蛋餃子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76543b12e8e91fa2e0ac7776072312926dd9e569","tid":903492,"uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b873d5ad2dff3c52c09e5696245b1a839eefb9d","tid":903492,"uid":137895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"茄汁豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0bdf30e34f44e1c8736f283341011076105d0e","tid":903492,"uid":133911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea0d13253f0e7e9bfce7c1878df652e67f085f40","tid":903492,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci